 <purpose>
This part of ISO 10303 specifies an application module for the representation of a rectangular array of patches.
   
 </purpose>

 <inscope>
   <li>trimming a surface to produce a topologically rectangular patch; </li>
  <li>defining the state of geometric continuity between patches in a surface; </li>
  <li>the definition of a bounded surface as a rectangular array of patches. </li>
  </inscope>

 <outscope>
   <li>
     bounded surfaces with curved boundaries.     
   </li>
 </outscope>

